  <brief_title>Effect of Multi-Media Enrollment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Investigation to Examine the Effect of a Multi-Media, Computer Based Tool (Talking Touchscreen) on Enrollment in Adult Oncology-Specific Clinical Trials at an Academic Medical Center</official_title>
